PN,36201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FA high school teacher has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of murdering and sexually
OL,8,Fabusing a 13-month-old baby he had
OL,9,Fadopted and treated as a "plaything".
OL,11,FJamie Varley, 37, adopted Preston
OL,12,FDavey, at nine-months-old with his
OL,13,Fpartner, ex-public schoolboy and
OL,14,Ffinancial sales manager, John McGowan-
OL,15,FFazakerley, 32.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FBut in the just under four months he
OL,7,Fwas in their care, at their home in
OL,8,FBlackpool, Preston was routinely ill-
OL,9,Ftreated, had indecent images and
OL,10,Fvideos taken of him, and was sexually
OL,11,Fabused and physically assaulted.
OL,13,FHe suffered 40 traumatic injuries
OL,14,Fbefore his death on 27 July 2023, the
OL,15,Ftrial at Preston Crown Court was told.
OL,17,FJurors spent around 14 hours
OL,18,Fconsidering verdicts before returning
OL,19,Fto court, after the eight-week trial,
OL,20,Fto deliver verdicts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FVarley was found guilty of murder, two
OL,7,Fcounts of assault by penetration, five
OL,8,Fcounts of cruelty to a child, grievous
OL,9,Fbodily harm, sexual assault of a
OL,10,Fchild, 13 counts of taking indecent
OL,11,Fphotos or videos of a child, one of
OL,12,Fdistributing an indecent photo of a
OL,13,Fchild, to his co-accused, and one of
OL,14,Fmaking an indecent photo.
OL,16,FMcGowan-Fazakerley was found guilty of
OL,17,Fallowing the death of a child, two
OL,18,Fcounts of child cruelty and one count
OL,19,Fof the sexual assault of a child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FVarley stood in the dock and put his
OL,7,Fhands to his face in shock as the
OL,8,Fguilty verdicts were read, before
OL,9,Fcollapsing to his knees, wretching and
OL,10,Fvomiting.
OL,12,FHis co-accused made no reaction, while
OL,13,FMcGowan-Fazakerley's father shook his
OL,14,Fhead.
OL,16,FPreston's mother and grandmother burst
OL,17,Finto tears, sobbing throughout as the
OL,18,F29 guilty verdicts were returned.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FPreston had been taken from his
OL,7,Fmother, Sarah Davey, now 42, by an
OL,8,Femergency care order by Oldham Council.
OL,10,FMs Davey, aged 14 at the time, had
OL,11,Fbeen jailed for the "unspeakably
OL,12,Fwicked" murder of a frail pensioner in
OL,13,F1998 and in and out of prison since
OL,14,Fthen.
OL,16,FThe court heard Preston, who was born
OL,17,Fon 16 June 2022, was placed into the
OL,18,Fcare of Varley and McGowan-Fazakerley
OL,19,Fin April 2023.
OL,26,@sD@UOUtD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FProsecutor Peter Wright KC told the
OL,7,Fcourt the baby boy's short life had
OL,8,F"more than its share of misfortune",
OL,9,Fbut Preston had been a "perfectly
OL,10,Fhealthy boy" before the defendants
OL,11,Fbegan the process of adopting him.
OL,13,FLess than four months later, at about
OL,14,F6.30pm on 27 July, he was brought to
OL,15,Fthe Accident and Emergency Department
OL,16,Fof Blackpool Victoria Hospital by the
OL,17,Fdefendants.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@cO]qD@XOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FHe was unconscious and in a state of
OL,7,Fcardiac arrest, despite medics
OL,8,Fattempts to revive him but he died
OL,9,Fless than an hour later.
OL,11,FA post-mortem found his death to be as
OL,12,Fa result either of a smothering with a
OL,13,Fhand or soft fabric or by the
OL,14,Finsertion of an object into his mouth.
OL,16,FMr Wright continued: "As terrible as
OL,17,Fit is, this tragedy was not the result
OL,18,Fof some dreadful yet unforeseen
OL,19,Faccident, or natural phenomenon.
OL,26,@xD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,F"The evidence gathered during the
OL,7,Finvestigation into his untimely death
OL,8,Frevealed a much more sinister
OL,9,Fpathology.
OL,11,F"We say the evidence demonstrates that
OL,12,Fhe was murdered by one of the people
OL,13,Fentrusted with his wellbeing; one of
OL,14,Fhis proposed adoptive parents.
OL,16,F"We say the person responsible for
OL,17,Fkilling Preston Davey was the
OL,18,Fdefendant, Jamie Varley."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,F"But that was not the only tragedy to
OL,7,Fbefall him when in the care of these
OL,8,Fdefendants," the prosecutor continued.
OL,10,F"In the final months of his brief
OL,11,Flife, we say he was routinely ill-
OL,12,Ftreated, sexually abused and
OL,13,Fphysically assaulted."
OL,15,FThe trial heard Preston had been taken
OL,16,Fto Blackpool Victoria Hospital three
OL,17,Ftimes in the months before his death
OL,18,Fwith suspicious bruises noticed by
OL,19,Fmedical staff, but these were
OL,20,Fexplained away and police stood down.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]rD@AOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FPreston had also been seen by multiple
OL,7,Fsocial workers and teachers,
OL,8,Fcolleagues of Varley, who took a year
OL,9,Foff work as head of year and design
OL,10,Fand technology teacher at South Shore
OL,11,FAcademy in Blackpool.
OL,13,FBut on 27 July 2023, Varley rushed
OL,14,FPreston to hospital a final time,
OL,15,Funresponsive.
OL,17,FHe claimed to have left the child in
OL,18,Fthe bath for a couple of minutes and
OL,19,Freturned to find him submerged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FAs medics worked for 50 minutes to
OL,7,Fsave his life, Varley gave a
OL,8,F"performance" of a grieving parent
OL,9,Fthat one senior doctor described as
OL,10,Funlike she had ever seen before, the
OL,11,Fcourt heard.
OL,13,FIt was also noted Preston's hair was
OL,14,Fdry, he had a nappy in place and he
OL,15,Fdid not appear to have swallowed any
OL,16,Fwater.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FA Home Office post-mortem ruled out
OL,7,Fdrowning as the cause of death and the
OL,8,Fexamination found around 40 non-
OL,9,Faccidental, internal and external
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FThey included multiple clusters of
OL,13,F'finger tip' bruises on his head, face
OL,14,Fand limbs, slap marks on his leg, and
OL,15,Fa human bite mark on the baby's right
OL,16,Fbuttock.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FPreston also had injuries to his
OL,7,Fmouth, throat and bottom, with parts
OL,8,Fof his anatomy "abnormal" and the
OL,9,Finjuries consistent with "forcible
OL,10,Fpenetration" and sexual abuse.
OL,12,FThe cause of Preston's death was found
OL,13,Fto be acute upper airways obstruction
OL,14,Fby an object or objects inserted into
OL,15,Fhis mouth.
OL,17,FA child safeguarding practice review,
OL,18,Fpaused during the criminal
OL,19,Fproceedings, will be re-launched by
OL,20,FOldham Council following the guilty
OL,21,Fverdicts.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@YO]qD@ZOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,FDetectives recovered evidence that
OL,7,FVarley had confessed to a fellow
OL,8,Fteacher about having "dark thoughts"
OL,9,Fof suffocating or drowning Preston.
OL,11,FHe had also sent a text to his sister
OL,12,Fsaying the child was "dead meat" after
OL,13,Fa sleepless night.
OL,15,FKaren Tonge, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,16,FService (CPS), said: "This has been
OL,17,Fone of the most shocking and horrific
OL,18,Fcases I have dealt with in my career.
OL,26,@pD@VOUpD@dO]tD@VOUtD@`O]xD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,F"Jamie Varley and John McGowan-
OL,7,FFazakerley had a responsibility to
OL,8,Fcare for and protect baby Preston.
OL,9,FThey violated that responsibility and
OL,10,F13-month-old Preston was abused with
OL,11,Fsickening ease.
OL,13,F"It is difficult to comprehend how the
OL,14,Fvery people who should have loved him
OL,15,Fcould inflict such sickening physical
OL,16,Fand sexual harm on an innocent child.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,F"No child should have to go through
OL,7,Fwhat Preston went through in the last
OL,8,Ffour months of his short life and I
OL,9,Fcannot begin to imagine the toll this
OL,10,Fhas taken on those that loved Preston.
OL,11,FMy thoughts remain with them all."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Oldham Council
OL,14,Fsaid: "The death of any child is a
OL,15,Ftragedy, but this is a particularly
OL,16,Fheart-wrenching and disturbing case.
OL,18,F"We are thankful that the perpetrators
OL,19,Fof the sickening murder and abuse of
OL,20,Fan innocent child have today been
OL,21,Fconvicted for their crimes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@bO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781599694
OL,3,CHigh school teacher guilty of sexually
OL,4,Cabusing and murdering baby boy
OL,6,F"An independent Child Safeguarding
OL,7,FPractice Review is already underway,
OL,8,Fwhich will examine the handling of
OL,9,FPreston's safeguarding.
OL,11,F"Our thoughts remain with Preston's
OL,12,Ffamily, loved ones, and the many
OL,13,Fpeople affected by this case."
OL,15,FBoth defendants will be sentenced on
OL,16,F18 July.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/17
